    65                              <1> ; Populate app_blob_base_v / size_v from VBE_INFO+0x20/+0x28 (filled by the
    66                              <1> ; UEFI loader after reading APPS.BIN). Falls back to the (now-zeroed) embedded
    67                              <1> ; symbols if no blob was loaded — in that case the apps are effectively absent
